{"tid":2448387,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"布林肯以「國家」稱呼台灣是否為口誤，外人無法核實","createTime":"2021-03-16T01:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T01:31:24.000Z","uid":179729,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"caac24662de9c55cf126dae32cd864109d94a587","tid":2448387,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>中美高層會談前夕：美國多次公開評論台灣議題引發議論</strong><br />\n<br />\n眾所矚目的美中高層對話即將於周四（3月18日）在美國阿拉斯加舉行。外界分析，除了美中經貿問題將是對話核心之外，南海和台灣議題也會是對話焦點之一。後者可從這幾天，美方高層對於台海議題的陸續評論可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n3月10日，美國國務卿布林肯（Antony Blinken）在眾議院答詢時承諾，將邀請台灣參與美國總統拜登（Joe Biden）籌劃的民主峰會（Summit for Democracy）之外，他又以「國家」（country）代稱台灣，引起外界許多討論。<br />\n<br />\n澳大利亞國立大學（ANU）亞太學院講師宋文笛向BBC中文分析，布林肯此舉似乎是華府在試探北京反應。他認為，布林肯以「國家」稱呼台灣是否為口誤，外人無法核實，而且重要性不大。宋文笛說，「但若是『有意口誤』，則進則是拜登團隊或許是在試水溫，退則是布林肯在阿拉斯加會議前夕，預先虛晃一招，拉開戰略縱深，以預留一步和累積籌碼。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-56400090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-56400090&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirInGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=dbeda4fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-56400090&h=ed16ec79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-56400090</a>"},{"pid":"77599ee49ae02e1064b6f1eea3d7a0768d5c0bb2","tid":2448387,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:22:09.000Z","msg":"All talk All action"},{"pid":"2410d0247912b7e1f8822a4506f0e8849acec888","tid":2448387,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"77599ee49ae02e1064b6f1eea3d7a0768d5c0bb2","tid":2448387,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:22:09.000Z","msg":"All talk All action"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:23:10.000Z","msg":"黃世柒ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50332516583417aba3ec921c2a00666ef3b1384d","tid":2448387,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewstrad/posts/4404664182883551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbbcnewstrad%2Fposts%2F4404664182883551&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirInGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=c34a8b80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewstrad/posts/4404664182883551</a>"},{"pid":"b1c9b6383bd823ed3ee4a9ee6ed820c26f754f8f","tid":2448387,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:25:44.000Z","msg":"不過連登之前都有討論過呢件事<br />\n<br />\n有人認為英國其實都分為四個country<br />\n所以叫country其實冇乜咁值得打J"},{"pid":"837070e84e8094994d7edc4498be20838f84c48d","tid":2448387,"uid":60057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D鬼佬好似STATE同COUNTRY有唔同MEANING"},{"pid":"3bc218b4e54eda065a9c302800d3970c581a71ff","tid":2448387,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1c9b6383bd823ed3ee4a9ee6ed820c26f754f8f","tid":2448387,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:25:44.000Z","msg":"不過連登之前都有討論過呢件事<br />\n<br />\n有人認為英國其實都分為四個country<br />\n所以叫country其實冇乜咁值得打J"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:31:24.000Z","msg":"咁之前美國係點樣稱呼台灣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}